{
  "stem": "5758.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, you see, I had to judge myself, whether it is better to be tortured and maybe under torture, to tell them names of the resistance group that I was, was.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Or whether it was, was better to tell the truth.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I didn't want to get tortured.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I didn't want to get-- didn't know whether I could stand pain.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I-- so they, they said-- I, I judged, rightly or wrongly.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This is-- I knew I wouldn't get free.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because somehow or other, the French knew I had a, had a false identification paper.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they told the German that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so it was-- What was going to be the  lesser of two evils.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's right, lesser of the two evils.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At that time, naturally, we didn't know what happens to Jews.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, you know, maybe, maybe we heard that they are going to work in Germany or something.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But we didn't know of the atrocities.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So they told us that from time to time, there is going to be on the board, names on it, for transport to work in Germany.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they all said, you will be working in Germany.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You will be together with your families.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Well, I didn't have family then.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But some-- very often, when they got whole families together and [INAUDIBLE] children and this here, the children were together in one room.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The parents, the women were together in one room, and the men separately.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not since then.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not-- no, once I was arrested, no way.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But also when I was hiding up in the hills, I wouldn't go and tell them where I am, naturally.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
